OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,FAn 'idiot' driver overtook numerous
OL,7,Fcars on the wrong side of the road
OL,8,Fwhile driving twice the speed limit -
OL,9,Fbefore crashing into an elderly
OL,10,Fcouple's vehicle, killing a man.
OL,12,FCaleb Mansfield-Marr, 22, sped up to
OL,13,Fthe junction of Ashton Road and
OL,14,FLingard lane in Bredbury, Stockport,
OL,15,Fin August last year. A woman felt her
OL,16,Fcar 'shake' as he drove past, while
OL,17,Fanother driver said he was 'driving
OL,18,Flike an idiot'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
