OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,FAs grandparents Jack and Judith Howe
OL,7,Fturned right onto Lingard Lane,
OL,8,FMansfield-Marr crashed into them head-
OL,9,Fon.
OL,11,FMr Howe, 76, was left with serious
OL,12,Finternal injuries and sadly died weeks
OL,13,Flater. His wife of 50-years was left
OL,14,Fwith serious injuries, but made a full
OL,15,Frecovery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
