OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,FMansfield-Marr, from Hyde, was also
OL,7,Fhurt and posted a picture online of
OL,8,Fhis injuries. Police later found
OL,9,Fvideos on his phone - including one in
OL,10,Fwhich he filmed himself driving with
OL,11,Fhis feet hanging out of the window.
OL,13,FHe later pleaded guilty to causing
OL,14,Fdeath by dangerous driving; causing
OL,15,Fserious injury by dangerous driving;
OL,16,Fand causing death by driving while
OL,17,Fdisqualified and without insurance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
