OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,FProsecutor Robert Smith told Minshull
OL,7,FStreet Crown COurt that at around
OL,8,F11.20am on August 5, Mrs Howe was
OL,9,Fdriving her Toyota Aygo along Ashton
OL,10,FRoad in Bredbury when she approached
OL,11,Fthe junction with Lingard Lane. Her
OL,12,Fhusband Jack was in the passenger seat.
OL,14,FShe gave way to several cars before
OL,15,Fmaking the turn. Mansfield-Marr,
OL,16,Fdriving a VW Polo in the opposite
OL,17,Fdirection, had already overtaken two
OL,18,Fcars on the wrong side of the road at
OL,19,Fspeeds of 64mph. The road was governed
OL,20,Fby 30mph limit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
