OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,FShe suffered from a number of injuries
OL,7,Fincluding a broken pelvis and ribs,
OL,8,Fand was treated and discharged after
OL,9,Feight weeks. Mr Howe suffered multiple
OL,10,Finjuries to his body. CT scans later
OL,11,Fshowed significant wounds to his
OL,12,Fspleen as well as a collapsed lung.
OL,14,FDespite the best efforts of medical
OL,15,Fstaff, he died on September 25.
OL,16,FMansfield-Marr was also injured and
OL,17,Ftaken to hospital. He later took a
OL,18,Fpicture of himself and uploaded it
OL,19,Fonline with the caption: "Fractured
OL,20,Fspine...chipped tooth...cut on head...
OL,21,Fold man pulled out."
OL,26,@{D@ZOU}D@TO]
