OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,FHe was later arrested and interviewed
OL,7,Fand his phone was seized. Officers
OL,8,Ffound a number of videos in which he
OL,9,Fhad filmed himself driving.
OL,11,FOne video showed him driving at 80mph
OL,12,Fin the motorway in cruise control with
OL,13,Fhis feet out of the driver's window.
OL,14,FIn another he filmed himself doing
OL,15,Fdoughnuts in a car park and another
OL,16,Fshowed him overtaking other cars.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
