OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,FSpeaking of her husband's death, Mrs
OL,7,FHowe said: "The morning of 25
OL,8,FSeptember 2023 changed my life
OL,9,Fforever, I became a widow. My lovely
OL,10,Fkind and caring husband of fifty years
OL,11,Fhad passed away. No more
OL,12,Fcompanionship, conversations, laughs
OL,13,For celebrations to share together.
OL,15,F"I am healing from my injuries, but
OL,16,Fnothing can heal my loss of losing
OL,17,FJack, my husband and my best friend."
OL,18,FTheir son, Richard, said: "Our world
OL,19,Ffeels like a dark place without his
OL,20,Flight," he said.
