OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,FSarah, their daughter, said she had
OL,7,Fdriven past the collision but did not
OL,8,Frealise it was her parents. "He was a
OL,9,Fkind, doting and supportive man, and
OL,10,Fsomeone I looked up to. I don't think
OL,11,FI will recover from this," she added.
OL,13,FAnd their third child, Louise, said:
OL,14,F"Our family structure is fractured, we
OL,15,Fare not able to regroup and never will
OL,16,F- there will always be one missing
OL,17,Fpiece."
