OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,FThe court heard that Mansfield-Marr
OL,7,Fhad previous driving matters on his
OL,8,Frecord including for speeding and
OL,9,Ffailing to provide driver details. He
OL,10,Fwas banned at the time for six months.
OL,12,FAn image later recovered from his
OL,13,Fphone showed Mansfield-Marr holding
OL,14,Fthe letter informing him he was
OL,15,Fdisqualified next to a gas hob, the
OL,16,Fcourt heard.
OL,18,FMitigating, John Dye said his client
OL,19,Fhad written multiple letters to the
OL,20,Ffamily of Mr Howe apologising for his
OL,21,Fbehaviour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
