OL,3,C"He acted so brazenly, not caring that
OL,4,Che could be caught."
OL,6,F"This is a dangerous man who believes
OL,7,Fthe rules and laws that all other road
OL,8,Fusers abide by daily do not apply to
OL,9,Fhim. At the time of the collision, he
OL,10,Fwas a disqualified driver, but even
OL,11,Fthat did not deter him from driving
OL,12,Fdangerously and at speeds that were
OL,13,Fwholly inappropriate for the
OL,14,Fconditions. He acted so brazenly, not
OL,15,Fcaring that he could be caught.
